data.description: This 4-bedroom, 2-bath manufactured home sits on a spacious .50 acre lot, offering lots of space to park boats, campers and etc. The master suite is a retreat, featuring a cozy sunroom perfect for morning or evening relaxation. It has a large master bath with separate tub and shower with double sinks. The closets in all bedrooms are lined with cedar. The home offers two living rooms and one featuring a fireplace. The dining room and kitchen allows for seamless entertaining, makes meals more practical and enjoyable. IT also offers a front porch and a rear screened porch, a fully fenced back yard and two RV hook-ups. One is a 30 amp and the other is a 50 amp hook-up. Located on a quiet circle but still only minutes from all Steinhatchee has to offer. More photos to come.
